## SUMMARY

In brief:
- We collect minimal personal data: email address and password hash for authentication
- We collect technical data: IP addresses, device tokens, widget/dashboard configurations
- We do NOT collect your name, phone number, physical address, or payment information (unless you provide it)
- We do NOT sell your data to third parties
- We do NOT use third-party analytics in the App (only App Store standard statistics)
- We do NOT share your data for marketing purposes
- You can request deletion of your data at any time

